{"id": "1475354903701356564", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "關於我覺得薩爾瓦多的原型並不是伊格但確實可能有一點烏波薩斯拉（很少）\n但我跑去看電影了所以我慢慢打", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T04:53:39.811000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:38:47.620000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "Murphy_satisfy", "emoji_id": "1468258389850193960", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475356176450326665", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "先放結論\n我個人覺得神父本體是取了點烏波薩拉斯石板的部分但他整體構成更多的還是基督教&聖經元素（應該蠻明顯", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T04:58:43.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475356334835765403", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "是說他外型就很耶穌了（愛老頭", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T04:59:21.020000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475407281133719663", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "聖堂教會很明顯在neta基督教/天主教\n我就簡單把自己認得的天主教元素打出來而已因為我也不是教徒所以沒那麼熟(資料會截圖維基百科因為好找", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:21:47.564000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475407503020789760", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "## 1. 十誡石板", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:22:40.466000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475408940974997605", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "這個應該蠻明顯的，十誡的故事可能大部分人也多少聽過，摩西在西奈山上獲得了十誡的石板。\n而且「刻有神秘文字的石板」這點剛好可以和烏波薩斯拉牽上一點線。照這樣看說不定聖堂教會雖然是在neta天主教但神父認為的父神其實就是烏波薩斯拉。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:28:23.301000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475408941109481512", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 164276, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475408941109481512/image.png?ex=69ccd727&is=69cb85a7&hm=6c40bbb75e6429611c2230af985223da3f5306fdaab423375cfc43fc8c2a03cd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475410982632423476", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "## 2.  耶穌寶血/聖餐", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:36:30.070000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:41:11.939000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475413769357230242", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "聖餐的由來是基督在被出賣的那一夜，與門徒最後的晚餐上拿出了葡萄酒和餅分給眾人。\n「耶穌拿起餅來祝福，就擘開，遞給門徒說，你們拿著吃，這是我的身體。又拿起杯來，祝謝了，遞給他們說，你們都喝這個，因為這是我立約的血，為多人流出來，使罪得赦。」(馬太福音26章)", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:47:34.477000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475415091988922420", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然聖餐禮在彌薩中主要是用作紀念耶穌的犧牲，但在教義中耶穌的血肉(主要是血)，為了教徒而流的血是有救贖意義的。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:52:49.817000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475415091813027961", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 91936, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475415091813027961/image.png?ex=69ccdce1&is=69cb8b61&hm=026be43d33c1865a9fee3138362c433884aa566a4fea2c7414b8a51565b6a913&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475416784608952444", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "從神父的故事中可以得知生前神父的血就具有「賜福」，雖然具體的功效好像沒有明講，但推測大概率是減緩融蝕症狀?\n而據他所說這對他也是有副作用的，但他把這視為「代替眾人受苦」。很符合基督為了世人流血的描寫。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T08:59:33.369000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475416784474476554", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 103620, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475416784474476554/image.png?ex=69ccde75&is=69cb8cf5&hm=1aef49fa98a19f44ecb12f4c756a45fd1ea7663db192adab80929e4943b47f3f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475430256536981605", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "## 2.5. 神蹟與復活", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T09:53:05.327000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475432074516238376", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得這個就比較不是那麼重要了所以放2.5\n單純就是神父身上真的很多耶穌的影子而已\n像是行神蹟的部分\n除了醫病，復活死人，最有名的還有水上行走和五餅二魚\n但放在神父身上就是醫病吧。\n除此之外感覺成為喚醒體也可以說是一種死後三日復活", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:00:18.767000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475432073912127659", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 71625, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475432073912127659/image.png?ex=69ccecb2&is=69cb9b32&hm=1c294833416e75b40e05883f002decd395eeaf492463d7372c792f49a4e42619&"}, {"id": "1475432074256318555", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 101726, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475432074256318555/image.png?ex=69ccecb2&is=69cb9b32&hm=fe37e1a54ef1ea03f0a34b44fc254140c8c45f1cae84b21dc059d0457da4158a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475432341219446814", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "## 3. 伊甸園的蛇", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:01:22.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475433123138371779", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "終於來到這裡了，為甚麼我認為神父他的原型中並沒有伊格。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:04:28.778000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475434405525983323", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "首先，遊戲裡伊格的位置應該毫無疑問是阿爾比諾了。而目前遊戲中除了雙子設定(莉莉/希洛、汀克特/菲茵特、波魯克斯/卡斯托爾)以外，並沒有共享原型的案例(應該吧!)\n所以我並不覺得神父的原型中包含了伊格。\n\n那他的尾巴是哪來的呢?\n我認為就是縫了那條大名鼎鼎的--伊甸園之蛇。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:09:34.523000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475435828053282937", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:15:13.680000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475435827478921236", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 32047, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475435827478921236/image.png?ex=69ccf031&is=69cb9eb1&hm=172727e0e36d8096f4dfa82dad42544bf8d7742477b1de470d340474a87b2238&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475439663278723206", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "這條蛇目前普遍被認為是惡魔的化身，也可以說是誘惑的化身。牠誘惑亞當和夏娃偷食禁果，換句話說就是引誘人犯罪。\n而從神父的PV裡我們可以大概知道，那些被他拯救的人在最後一段中表現出了渴求更多賜福、甚至是怪罪他的狀態。\n神父是被判為異端後火刑，再結合他自己也說了人太多救不過來和neta耶穌這點，難免讓人聯想他是被人背叛後舉報成了異端(事實上耶穌在世時基督教也確實是異端)。\n\n儘管神父本人無意，但他的存在確實是讓人犯了罪(忌妒、背叛、陷害)。\n從某種意義上來說，他既是行神蹟的救世主也是引人犯罪的蛇。", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:30:28.069000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1475439663060881530", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 92310, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1475354903701356564/1475439663060881530/image.png?ex=69ccf3c4&is=69cba244&hm=90974061688b49ffeca8e0268cb3b56b619227702b784a6eb53db5930e844338&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1475440544996921486", "channel_id": "1475354903701356564", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "------------------------------------\n\n大概就這樣我講完了😭 之前看到很多人都在猜神父是不是有混伊格，我就很想大叫基督教裡也有隻蛇😭 \n反正都是我的猜測，就醬......😭", "timestamp": "2026-02-23T10:33:58.287000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475354903701356564", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我要蓋一個毫無根據的神父原型樓在這裡（很短的樓", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
